---
@META
dir: helm/ucebnice/templates
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 13
stack: Helm templates, Kubernetes YAML

@EXPORTS
_helpers.tpl: helpers — Helm template helper functions (fullname, labels, selectors)
deployment.yaml: Deployment — Next.js app (replicas, image, env, probes, resources)
service.yaml: Service — ClusterIP for app
ingress.yaml: Ingress — NGINX ingress with TLS termination
configmap.yaml: ConfigMap — non-secret configuration
secret.yaml: Secret — app environment secrets
hpa.yaml: HPA — horizontal pod autoscaler (CPU/memory based, 2-10 replicas)
pdb.yaml: PDB — pod disruption budget (minAvailable: 1)
serviceaccount.yaml: ServiceAccount — pod identity
postgres-statefulset.yaml: StatefulSet — PostgreSQL 15 with persistent volume
postgres-service.yaml: Service — PostgreSQL ClusterIP on port 5432
postgres-secret.yaml: Secret — database credentials
data-pvc.yaml: PVC — persistent volume claim for video/upload data

@STANDARDS
- All templates use _helpers.tpl for naming consistency
- PostgreSQL deployed alongside app in same namespace
- Health checks use /api/health endpoint
